document_data.mainbody: '''Jalathleena''' was a mysterious planeswalking [[Chosen of Mystra]] who departed [[Toril]] by the 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.History: Jalathleena found her magic gifts to be most useful in traversing the planes. She loved planar travel and petitioned with her deity, the Mother of All Magic, to venture into the vast multiverse on her behalf, procuring items, [[spell]]s, [[enchanted|wondrous item]]s, plants, and sentient creatures, bringing them to [[Faer√ªn]] and lands beyond.
